[[Info]] is 

# a program for reading manuals such as the EmacsManual as hypertext documents,
# the name of a computer file format for hypertext manuals, and 
# an Emacs mode for reading Info files (See InfoMode).

The recommended way to create Info files is to author documentation using [[Texinfo]].

See also [[InfoHistory]].

